section.t:
The ability to interconnect multiple content delivery networks (CDNs) has many benefits, including increased coverage, capability, and reliability. The Content Delivery Networks Interconnection (CDNI) framework   defines four interfaces to achieve interconnection of CDNs: (1)
      the CDNI Request Routing Interface; (2) the CDNI Metadata Interface;
       (3) the CDNI Logging Interface; and (4) the CDNI Control Interface.
